    </div>`;
  } else {
    vacEl.innerHTML = `<div class="callout cl-green"><span class="callout-ic">🎉</span><div class="callout-txt"><strong>Lahat ng kwarto occupied!</strong> 0 vacancy cost this month.</div></div>`;
